{"tid":2017072,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【官方自爆】中國這座建築內，關著世界最致命的各種病毒，也是亞洲唯一一座","createTime":"2020-05-15T01:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T02:49:18.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03e98fd03347991be78245f59980de463966e8f9","tid":2017072,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:17:16.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dL3VUdBxM8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdL3VUdBxM8s&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=66fdb4bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dL3VUdBxM8s</a>"},{"pid":"8a5706b2afd4dfa08d9f4764f9c83dbec06b3f14","tid":2017072,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:17:50.000Z","msg":"P4??"},{"pid":"428cb542de6351149c56555724e13426fca55a68","tid":2017072,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a5706b2afd4dfa08d9f4764f9c83dbec06b3f14","tid":2017072,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:17:50.000Z","msg":"P4??"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:18:27.000Z","msg":"片入面內文講晒"},{"pid":"7c267b4e0d89e00683da53797bd4fc9504afc6d6","tid":2017072,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"428cb542de6351149c56555724e13426fca55a68","tid":2017072,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a5706b2afd4dfa08d9f4764f9c83dbec06b3f14","tid":2017072,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:17:50.000Z","msg":"P4??"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:18:27.000Z","msg":"片入面內文講晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:20:17.000Z","msg":"仲講埋嚴格設計<br />\n只要有很少的意外洩漏，後果都係災難性的<br />\n仲講左一個外國例子，搞到千人感染"},{"pid":"f7d8e8c02d35f772a649a140026cd056702f9960","tid":2017072,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"講到咁嚴謹<br />\n跟住支那人都係可以岀事<br />\nDllm唔識做就咪鬼起啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63ea933e437cbb6354131c77a96c8f9b7c98b6b","tid":2017072,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7d8e8c02d35f772a649a140026cd056702f9960","tid":2017072,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"講到咁嚴謹<br />\n跟住支那人都係可以岀事<br />\nDllm唔識做就咪鬼起啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:05:47.000Z","msg":"唔起無疫苗研究<br />\n<br />\n好似有人爆過料<br />\n話有人專登去深山野嶺搵蝙蝠帶的病毒出黎研究<br />\n我個人認為唔好專登去野外搵病毒出黎就得<br />\n要研究全部係在人類現時curriculate緊的病毒研究"},{"pid":"02c1275d28527cb5162f6f31043ced2d5a78bbf8","tid":2017072,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:06:55.000Z","msg":"片入面內容：<br />\n1）只有好好研究病毒，才能找出對付病毒的好方法<br />\n2）世衛將病毒危害程度分為四級<br />\nBSL-1：大學的病毒實驗室，低傳染性和低危害性，無需特殊防禦措施，只要勤洗手便可<br />\nBSL-2：設生物危害標誌，研究人員需要保護衣，像甲型肝炎和乙型肝炎病毒，就是在BSL-2級實驗室中研究<br />\nBSL-3：病毒的傳染性和危害性更強，例如SARS冠狀病毒就是這類。<br />\nBSL-4：最高等級的病毒，病原體非常危險，人類對它的了解很少，如伊波拉病毒，就係呢個等級<br />\n3）這個實驗室位於武漢，屬BSL-4級<br />\n4）病毒實驗室保安設計極嚴密，進入核心區，要過十度門，其中七度門是互鎖的。<br />\n5）實驗室只要有很少的意外洩漏，後果都係災難性的<br />\n6）仲講左一個外國例子，就係1979年中東實驗室洩漏碳疽病毒，雖然只係屬BSL-3，且洩漏不足一克，但已搞到千人死亡。<br />\n7）實驗室的工作人員，即使在嚴密保安下，病發比率也比普通人高5至7倍。因此向實驗人員致崇高敬意。"},{"pid":"51500b321adbfa39c2c035437c4781e5cc8c43fa","tid":2017072,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd67731477e7f9972ce390e81475fa5784da0558","tid":2017072,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba4984af72cba0d16b589b0b8a8b228661036f2","tid":2017072,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:49:18.000Z","msg":"人間傳染的病原微生物名錄<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://2018.igem.org/wiki/images/3/34/T--SUSTech_Shenzhen--List.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2018.igem.org%2Fwiki%2Fimages%2F3%2F34%2FT--SUSTech_Shenzhen--List.pdf&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=a4950fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://2018.igem.org/wiki/images/3/34/T--SUSTech_Shenzhen--List.pdf</a>"}]}